# Skill Hub Design System

Inspired by ChainGPT Labs: dark-first, minimal, tech-forward with a vibrant orange accent.

## Color Palette

Use these Tailwind classes or CSS variables ŌĆö never hardcode raw hex values:

| Token | CSS var | Tailwind approx | Hex |
|-------|---------|-----------------|-----|
| Background primary | `--bg-primary` | `bg-[#0a0a0a]` | `#0a0a0a` |
| Background surface | `--bg-surface` | `bg-[#111111]` | `#111111` |
| Background card | `--bg-card` | `bg-[#161616]` | `#161616` |
| Border default | `--border` | `border-[#2a2a2a]` | `#2a2a2a` |
| Border subtle | `--border-subtle` | `border-[#1e1e1e]` | `#1e1e1e` |
| Text primary | `--text-primary` | `text-white` | `#ffffff` |
| Text secondary | `--text-secondary` | `text-[#a0a0a0]` | `#a0a0a0` |
| Text muted | `--text-muted` | `text-[#555555]` | `#555555` |
| **Accent orange** | `--accent` | `text-[#f47645]` | `#f47645` |
| Accent orange bg | `--accent-bg` | `bg-[#f47645]` | `#f47645` |
| Accent orange subtle | `--accent-subtle` | `bg-[#f47645]/10` | `#f4764519` |
| Accent orange border | `--accent-border` | `border-[#f47645]/30` | `#f4764550` |
| Green (ACTIVE) | ŌĆö | `text-[#4ade80]` | `#4ade80` |
| Yellow (INACTIVE) | ŌĆö | `text-[#facc15]` | `#facc15` |
| Red (SUSPENDED) | ŌĆö | `text-[#f87171]` | `#f87171` |

## Typography

- **Hero headings**: `text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-white`
- **Section labels**: `text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#f47645]`
- **Card titles**: `text-base font-semibold text-white`
- **Body / descriptions**: `text-sm text-[#a0a0a0]`
- **Monospace / IDs**: `font-mono text-xs text-[#555555]`
- **Price / highlight numbers**: `text-lg font-black text-white`

## Cards

```tsx
// Standard card
<div className="rounded-xl border border-[#2a2a2a] bg-[#161616] p-6 hover:border-[#f47645]/40 transition-colors">
```

```tsx
// Accent / featured card (e.g. RegisterBox)
<div className="rounded-xl border border-[#f47645]/30 bg-[#f47645]/5 p-6">
```

## Background Grid

The full-page grid is defined in `globals.css` ŌĆö do not override it on individual components:

```css
/* subtle square grid matching ChainGPT Labs */
background-image:
  linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
  linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
background-size: 40px 40px;
background-attachment: fixed;
```

## Buttons

Primary buttons use **black text on orange** (exact ChainGPT Labs style):

Chamfered-corner (45┬░ cut) outline button ŌĆö defined via `clip-chamfer` utility in `globals.css`.
Use a two-layer pattern: outer `div` provides the border color, inner `button` provides the dark fill.

```tsx
// Chamfered outline button
<div className="clip-chamfer bg-white/30 p-px w-fit hover:bg-white/60 transition-colors">
  <button className="clip-chamfer bg-[#0a0a0a] px-8 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-widest">
    ACTION
  </button>
</div>
```

For an orange-accented variant swap `bg-white/30` ŌåÆ `bg-[#f47645]/50` and `bg-white/60` ŌåÆ `bg-[#f47645]/80`.

## Badges / Pills

```tsx
// Trust / status badge
<span className="rounded-full border border-[#f47645]/30 bg-[#f47645]/10 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-[#f47645]">
```

## Navigation

- Height `py-4`, sticky top, `border-b border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0a0a0a]/95 backdrop-blur`
- Logo: `font-black text-white` with orange dot or accent mark
- Links: `text-sm text-[#a0a0a0] hover:text-white transition-colors`

## Layout

- Max content width: `max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4`
- Section gap: `space-y-12` or `gap-12`
- Card grid: `grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3`
- Section labels precede every major group with the accent label pattern above

## Do / Don't

Ō£ģ Use `#f47645` as the sole accent color ŌĆö replace indigo/purple/blue with orange  
Ō£ģ Keep backgrounds very dark (`#0a0a0a` ŌåÆ `#161616` surface stack)  
Ō£ģ Use generous whitespace ŌĆö avoid cramped layouts  
Ō£ģ Uppercase, bold, wide-tracked labels for section headers  
Ō£ģ Subtle border glow `border-[#f47645]/40` on hover states  
ŌØī Don't use `bg-gray-900` / `bg-gray-950` ŌĆö use the explicit hex tokens above  
ŌØī Don't use `indigo-`, `blue-`, or `purple-` for primary UI elements  
ŌØī Don't mix multiple accent colors ŌĆö orange only  
